<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1193165' id='t-1193165'>nobody, I mean, you dig it,
nobody gonna step on their turf.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1196072' id='t-1196072'>But we gotta be careful,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1197248' id='t-1197248'>'cause they can shoot around here too
