20:12
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1201223' id='t-1201223'>So that's the same concept.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1202545' id='t-1202545'>Then again, sometimes
economists get it wrong.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1204783' id='t-1204783'>One thing we observed in the data
