20:28
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1217258' id='t-1217258'>We had some theories related to cash flow,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='1219432' id='t-1219432'>and lack of access to capital markets,
